_sText:
Little map where your opponent can be EVERYWHERE AT ANY TIME of the fight : keep cool or you're dead :p

Climb up any where you want, the way that you want, like spiderman lol ^^ , that can be very pervers for your opponent when you roxx jumping in every direction FROM a ladder

Waypoint included but not interesting for this gameplay (bot can't use ladder like us)

Tests have been very exciting for now, I hope you'll enjoy as well !!!
